00:00:13.400 --> 00:00:14.333
of duho

00:00:15.466 --> 00:00:17.500
from Hispaniola

00:00:17.566 --> 00:00:19.666
but also from Jamaica and other places

00:00:20.300 --> 00:00:22.600
and I wanted to take pictures of all of them

00:00:25.466 --> 00:00:27.400
with the possibility in mind

00:00:28.066 --> 00:00:30.366
of a temporary exhibition in Santo Domingo

00:00:30.400 --> 00:00:32.866
which I later realized as director of the Museo del Hombre

00:00:33.333 --> 00:00:34.500
and there I was surprised

00:00:35.133 --> 00:00:36.266
I saw this image

