I asked the museum to send me

00:00:44.100 --> 00:00:44.900
the photos

00:00:45.533 --> 00:00:46.766
so when I received them

00:00:47.366 --> 00:00:49.566
it was what interested me the most

00:00:49.800 --> 00:00:50.800
they told me no

00:00:51.166 --> 00:00:53.500
it is not here and we do not know how it got here

00:00:55.066 --> 00:00:56.666
we simply have the photograph

00:00:57.266 --> 00:01:00.600
then I realized that Cambiaso

00:01:01.166 --> 00:01:01.966
was Italian

00:01:02.900 --> 00:01:05.200
and had been the owner of the artifact

00:01:05.766 --> 00:01:08.266
then I asked for a list of institutions

00:01:09.400 --> 00:01:11.266
archaeological and museum

00:01:12.066 --> 00:01:14.266
in Italy, especially in the area

00:01:15.300 --> 00:01:17.900
where the Cambiaso family came from

