Until I found someone who knew that piece

00:01:25.666 --> 00:01:26.733
which was in Turin

00:01:27.333 --> 00:01:28.600
then I wrote to Turin

00:01:28.800 --> 00:01:29.600
there, for a long time

00:01:29.900 --> 00:01:32.700
they thought it was a Peruvian piece

00:01:32.866 --> 00:01:34.866
at some point

00:01:35.066 --> 00:01:37.133
they realized it was Caribbean

00:01:37.266 --> 00:01:38.466
but they did not give it importance

00:01:38.533 --> 00:01:39.800
until I finished my work

00:01:40.366 --> 00:01:43.200
in a way it was a coincidence

00:01:43.500 --> 00:01:45.566
why was that photograph in London?

00:01:45.966 --> 00:01:48.933
if that photo had not been in London

00:01:49.166 --> 00:01:51.566
who knows if today we would know

00:01:52.300 --> 00:01:53.466
where this piece is
